properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Pensacola FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Pensacola FL to Pascagoula MS out 20 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 9 at 10:08AM CST until February 10 at 3:00AM CST by NWS Mobile AL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southeast winds 20 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 2 to 5 ft.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Pensacola FL to Pascagoula MS out
20 NM and Coastal waters from Okaloosa Walton County Line FL
to Pensacola FL out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until 3 AM CST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM CST MONDAY
